'''Uccen''' d yiwwen uɣeṛsiw azagir yettidiren deg [[Tafriqt|Tefriqt]] akked [[Asya]], yettidir daɣen deg tmura n [[Turuft]] (Uṛup) i d-yezgan ɣer tama n yilel agrakal.<br>

Uccanen ttidiren d tiwaculin, tawacult tebna ɣef imarawen akked warraw (tarwa-nsen). Yal tawacult tesɛa aḥric-ines n tmurt, tessenqad-it daɣen tettɛassa-t. Tetten igumma (fruits), amurḍus d wayen ara d-gemren am iɣeṛsiwen imecṭaḥ, ibaɛac, igwra neɣ igdaḍ (oiseaux).<br>

Uccen itteffeɣ tikkwal ad yegmer iman-is ladɣa mi ara tili tewtemt-is s tadist, tikkwal-nniḍen ttefɣen deg sin neɣ gellun ula d arraw-nsen.<br>
 
Uccen izemmel tiḥeṛci akked tigzi deg yidelsan iɣeṛfanen.

